comments: Nurkic (POR) is already in Brooks' (MEM) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) is moving alongside Lillard's (POR) path and the marginal contact is caused by Lillard.
Brooks (MEM) and Nurkic (POR) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Nurkic (POR) turns into Morant's (MEM) body and delivers contact that affects his shot near the rim.
Allen (MEM) and McCollum (POR) make incidental foot to foot contact with one another on the perimeter.
Brooks (MEM) brings his arm down and makes marginal contact with Powell's (POR) shoulder as he defends the shot near the rim.
Allen (MEM) makes contact with Nurkic's (POR) body that affects his shot near the rim.
Brooks (MEM) cleanly blocks Lillard's (POR) shot near the rim.
Morant (MEM) is jumping alongside Lillard's (POR) path and legally contests the shot near the rim.
Covington (POR) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Morant (MEM) legally contests Powell's (POR) driving shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Nurkic (POR) is already in Brooks' (MEM) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Nurkic (POR) is already in Brooks' (MEM) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Lillard (POR) is bracing for the contact from Morant (MEM) and releases away from the contact.
Morant (MEM) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Powell (POR) commits a take foul on Allen (MEM).
Brooks (MEM) moves slightly forward towards McCollum (POR) on the perimeter and contact is marginal.
